snippet.textDisplay: This song is about embracing life’s journey with an open heart. The singer acknowledges that life is fleeting and unpredictable, but chooses to find happiness in the moment and ignore negativity. They cast off societal expectations and explore the world freely, though aware of the weight of past experiences. The song ends with a sense of wonder about life’s grand journey, full of both beauty and mystery and a hint of finding love along the way.
